timeline.bodyText:
I'd prefer all the repeated chain.doFilter(request, response) in a caller method. So rename the current method to doFilterIdempotent and then have:
@Override 
public void doFilter(...) throws ... {
    if (!doFilterIdempotent()) {
        chain.doFilter(request, response);
    }
}

And return false from doFilterIdempotent whenever you haven't done any processing.

